message.raw:
DisplayPlugins don't inherit from Plugin anymore

GUI Plugins represent standalone widgets, and DisplayPlugins are not a subclass of that.
DisplayPlugins have their own loading mechanism that is not piggy-backing on that for
ordinary GUI Plugins anymore.
